sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant IndividualProvidedDetailsController
    participant HMRC_Auth as HMRC Auth
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB (individual)

    Client->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: GET /individual-provided-details/by-id/{individualProvidedDetailsId}
    IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>HMRC_Auth: Authenticate (GG, Agent affinity)
    alt Auth fails
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: 401 Unauthorised
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 401 Unauthorised
    else Auth succeeds
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Authenticated
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>MongoDB: findOne(_id = individualProvidedDetailsId)
        alt Record found
            MongoDB-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: IndividualProvidedDetails
            IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 200 OK (IndividualProvidedDetails JSON)
        else Record not found
            MongoDB-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: None
            IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 204 No Content
        end
    end
